Class BoxJSONObject

  • Object
    • BoxJSONObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BoxEnterprise, BoxLock, BoxResource.Info, BoxSharedLink, BoxSharedLink.Permissions, BoxUploadEmail, EmailAlias

    public abstract class BoxJSONObject
extends Object
    The abstract base class for all types that contain JSON data returned by the Box API. The most common implementation of BoxJSONObject is BoxResource.Info and its subclasses. Changes made to a BoxJSONObject will be tracked locally until the pending changes are sent back to Box in order to avoid unnecessary network requests.
